item.title: BNL Rookies
item.description:
Some Vikings made their BNL debut against the Panthers this weekend ...

Congratulations to Cleve Dombas and Sivuyile "Bam" Mdekazi for making their Western Cape Mountaineers debuts this weekend.

Both of them did fantastically well, and have a bright future at the next level. Keep it up ballers!!!

Cleve, Bam, Godfrey and Maloti chilling before the game
